# Repo-wide ignores. Per-package ignores live in frontend/.gitignore and
# backend/.gitignore. This file only covers stuff that applies everywhere:
# OS metadata, editor state, and defensive .env catch-alls.

# ── OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# ── Editors / IDEs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.history/
.project
.classpath

# ── Defensive env catch-alls (per-package gitignores also cover these) ──
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Deploy tooling ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vercel/
.render/

# ── Logs anywhere ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Local planning / spec docs (uncomment to keep them out of the repo)
#    Delete or comment individual lines if you want to track any of them.
# /Instruction.md
# /TESTING.md
# /TESTING_DETAILS.md
# /Tendor_Dashboard.md
